{"tid":895305,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"霍金遺物拍賣價高過預期 輪椅600萬成交","createTime":"2018-11-09T05:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T09:04:58.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"11e290222188a4b7e40b044383b46fcc48a8448c","tid":895305,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T05:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181109/_2018110910370191024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181109%2F_2018110910370191024.jpg&h=1ddec82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">霍金生前的輪椅以高於估價30倍成交。資料圖片</span><br />\n<br />\n知名物理學家霍金（Stephen Hawking）今年3月逝世，日前拍賣行拍賣他生前22件遺物，包括生前坐的輪椅及論文，分別拍出29.6萬英鎊（約300萬港元）、58.5萬英鎊（約600萬港元），論文高於估價約3倍，輪椅甚至高於估價30倍。<br />\n<br />\n拍賣行指，霍金的遺物中，最受矚目的就是霍金生前使用的輪椅，因為霍金生前曾與該輪椅拍過MV，輪椅壓過英國王儲查爾斯的腳，還開玩笑說希望也能壓到前首相戴卓爾夫人，外界早前預估會以1萬至1.5萬英鎊（約15萬港元）的價格成交。其他拍賣品還有霍金以指紋簽名的著作《時間簡史》、曾客串的卡通《阿森一族》劇本等。<br />\n<br />\n拍賣會日前正式舉行，最後論文以58.5萬英鎊拍出，高於估價約3倍，輪椅則拍出了29.6萬英鎊，高於估價20至30倍，拍賣人員都大感意外，拍賣所得將會捐給霍金基金會及漸凍人協會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/860386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F860386&d=yxB5lvmTknxbtXs%2Bbw%2BYusKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=ed5c6232\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F860386&h=9e87219d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/860386</a>"},{"pid":"5147b706e98cdb207355f752f5b0e4f219a446cb","tid":895305,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"霍金急轉灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" c